  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-metal-copper": "若与石灰结合，可产生蓝色或绿色。单独使用铜会产生一种非常暗的红色、不透明的玻璃。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-metal-gold": "可用于釉料和涂层。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-metal-lead": "焙烧铅会生成铅氧化物，它是亮黄色和红色颜料的基础。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-metal-nickel": "可用于产生深蓝色、黑色或紫色。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-metal-rusty": "产生绿色、棕色、灰色甚至黑色。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-metal-silver": "可用于釉料。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-metal-temporal": "可能有助于制造发出蓝色或紫色光芒的物体。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-metal-tin": "加热锡会将其转化为锡氧化物，一种用于釉料的白色粉末。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-hematite": "粉末状铁氧化物，可产生橙色或红色。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-ilmenite": "可将生钛加入玻璃批次中，以产生更深的颜色。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-indigo": "可产生强烈的蓝色染料，无需媒染剂即可染料布料。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-kernite": "用水密封在木桶中，可将其转化为硼砂。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-lapislazuli": "研磨成细粉的青金石。可产生深蓝色。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-leadoxide": "红色与黄色铅氧化物的混合物。小心加热并冷却后，会变成亮黄色和红色颜料。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-limonite": "粉末状铁氧化物，可产生黄色或橙色。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-litharge": "一种呈鲜红色的铅氧化物形态。<br>用作颜料，为各种产品染色和着色。",
  "game:handbook-item-usage-powdered-ore-magnesiumhydroxide": "用于制备<a href=\"handbook://item-em:powdered-矿物-magnesiumoxide\">镁白</a>的前驱体。",
